projects.name: News Website-Flash Bulletin
projects.description: Developed a dynamic news website that aggregates and displays the latest news articles from various sources using a news API. Organizes articles into categories such as politics, technology, sports, and entertainment for easy navigation. Utilizes a news API to fetch real-time news articles from multiple reputable sources. Allows users to search for articles by keywords or topics. Clean and modern design with intuitive navigation and a focus on readability.

projects.name: Website of a Restaurant
projects.description: Designed and developed a website for Chillin Cafe to showcase the menu and enhance customer experience. Responsive design for seamless viewing on mobile and desktop devices. Displays dishes with detailed descriptions and prices, complemented by high-quality images. Allows customers to place online orders directly through the website. Stylish and intuitive design for seamless navigation and enhanced visual appeal.

projects.name: Portfolio Website
projects.description: Designed and developed a personal portfolio website to showcase professional projects and skills. Responsive design for seamless viewing on mobile and desktop devices. Integrated animations to enhance user experience.

experiences.description: Active member of the Bureau of Indian Standards (BIS) Club at MAIT. Participated in workshops and seminars focused on the importance of standardization and quality control in various industries. Engaged in activities aimed at promoting awareness and understanding of BIS standards among students and faculty. Assisted in organizing events, including guest lectures by industry experts and BIS representatives, to enhance knowledge of standards and compliance.

Actively contributed to the success of the International Symposium on Smart Cities, Technologies, and Trends through volunteer support. Assisted in event coordination and participant engagement. Gained valuable experience in event management and networking with industry professionals, enhancing my skills and knowledge in smart city technologies.
